text: State Route 167 (SR 167) is a state highway in the Seattle metropolitan area in the U.S. state of Washington. The highway's south end is at Interstate 5 (I-5) in Tacoma. Its north end is at SR 900 in Renton. The highway is long. The highway meets I-405 also in Renton. ==References== Category:Roads in Washington (state)
title: Washington State Route 167
